## <a id='upgrading'></a> Upgrade Path to the Latest Version

When upgrading PAS and SSO at the same time, follow the steps below in order:

1. If your SSO tile is not on your current PAS's recommended SSO version (see table below), upgrade it.
1. Upgrade PAS to the newer version.
1. If your SSO tile is not on the recommended version for the newer PAS version, upgrade the SSO tile.

