### <a id='upgrading-example'></a> Upgrade Example
If you are using SSO v1.6.0 and PAS v2.1.0 and want to upgrade to SSO v1.7.0 and PAS v2.2.x,
you do the following:

1. Upgrade to SSO v1.7.x on PAS v2.1.0, which is the recommended SSO version for PAS v2.1.0.
1. Upgrade PAS to v2.2.x (newer PAS version).
1. No further updgrade is needed because SSO is already at v1.7.x, which is the PAS v2.2.x supported SSO version.


